1. Komanda dlya ispolneniya scripta:
     chmod +x scan.py
     
2. Prosnotr spravki:
     python3 scan.py

3. Ustanovka mongodb dlya testirovaniya:
     sudo apt install mongodb -y

4. Zapusk mongodb:
     sudo systemctl start mongodb

5. Proverka chto mongodb zapushena:
     sudo systemctl status mongodb
--------------

 ZAPUSK SCANERA
 
6. Skanirovanie local'nogo hosta:
     python3 scan.py 127.0.0.1

7. Scan nestandartnogo porta:
     python3 scan.py 127.0.0.1 27018

8. Scan podseti:
     python3 scan.py 192.168.1.0/24

9. Ostanovka i ochistka:
     sudo systemctl stop mongodb
